---Mouse Bindings

right click on empty screen             brings up menu
left click on tag                       view tag
scroll on tag                           next/prev tag
scroll/click on layout                  cycle layouts
modkey + left click on tag              pin client to that tag only
modkey + right click on tag             pin/unpin client to that tag
right click on tag                      view multiple tags in same view
modkey + left click                     move window
modkey + right click                    resize window

---Key Bindings

modkey + control + r                    restart awesome
modkey + shift   + q                    quit awesome
modkey +         + r                    run command
modkey +         + return               start terminal (urxvtc)
modkey +         + w                    brings up menu

modkey +         + m                    toggle client full maximize/unmaximize
modkey +         + k                    toggle client horizontal maximize/unmaximize
modkey +         + j                    toggle client vertical maximize/unmaximize
modkey +         + ,                    minimize client
modkey + control + ,                    restore client from minimize
alt    +         + f                    toggle client fullscreen
modkey +         + c                    kill client
modkey +         + t                    toggle client on top even when not focused

modkey +         + left                 focus on next client
modkey +         + right                focus on previous client
modkey + control + left                 view next tag
modkey + control + right                view previous tag
modkey +         + 1-9                  switch to tag 1-9
modkey + alt     + left                 focus next screen
modkey + alt     + right                focus previous screen
modkey +         + tab                  client focus on last visited

alt    +         + left                 swap clients by ids next (change position in taskbar)
alt    +         + right                swap clients by ids previous (change position in taskbar)
modkey +         + o                    move focused client to next screen
modkey +         + l                    decrease master client width
modkey +         + h                    increase master client width
modkey + shift   + l                    decrease number of naster clients by 1
modkey + shift   + h                    increase number of naster clients by 1
modkey + control + l                    decrease number of columns for non-naster clients by 1
modkey + control + h                    increase number of columns for non-naster clients by 1
modkey +         + space                switch to next layout
modkey + shift   + space                switch to prev layout
modkey + control + space                toggle client floating
modkey + control + return               swap client to master
modkey + control + 1-9                  select multiple tags in one view
modkey + shift   + 1-9                  pin client to that tag only
modkey + shift + control + 1-9          pin/unpin client to that tag

modkey +         + b                    hide/show upper bar
modkey + alt     + b                    hide/show lower bar
printscreen                             take screenshot
modkey +         + x                    lock screen
